                <p> <%= link_to "Programme for 2019", "resource/FOPB_2019.pdf" %></p>
                <p>For further information please call or email, Stanley Lowy: 020 8657 3684 or stanlowy@outlook.com, Elizabeth Bennett: bennett_@sky.com, Mac Court: mac_court@talktalk.ne</p>
              </td>
