                <p>Meetings commence at 10.30 on the fourth Tuesday of the month at the United Reformed Church Hall, Sanderstead Hill, South Croydon, CR2 0HB.  Coffee is served from 9.45 to 10.15am.  The November meeting is ‘Food and Art Through the Ages' by Tasha Marks.</p>
                <p>At present there is no waiting list for new members joining and visitors are welcome on payment of a small fee. For more information phone 0208 660 9122. Email:  suedavenport72@gmail.com</p>
